<Link id="l00755" /><CodeLine lineNumber="755"><Highlight kind="normal">&#125;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00756" /><CodeLine lineNumber="756"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00757" /><CodeLine lineNumber="757"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// This function checks to see if an expansion of memcmp can be generated.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00758" /><CodeLine lineNumber="758"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// It checks for constant compare size that is less than the max inline size.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00759" /><CodeLine lineNumber="759"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// If an expansion cannot occur, returns false to leave as a library call.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00760" /><CodeLine lineNumber="760"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Otherwise, the library call is replaced with a new IR instruction sequence.</Highlight><Highlight kind="comment"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00761" /><CodeLine lineNumber="761"><Highlight kind="comment">/// We want to transform:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00762" /><CodeLine lineNumber="762"><Highlight kind="comment">/// %call = call signext i32 @memcmp(i8&#42; %0, i8&#42; %1, i64 15)</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00763" /><CodeLine lineNumber="763"><Highlight kind="comment">/// To:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00764" /><CodeLine lineNumber="764"><Highlight kind="comment">/// loadbb:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00765" /><CodeLine lineNumber="765"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %0 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer2 to i8&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00766" /><CodeLine lineNumber="766"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %1 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer1 to i8&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00767" /><CodeLine lineNumber="767"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %2 = bitcast i8&#42; %1 to i64&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00768" /><CodeLine lineNumber="768"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %3 = bitcast i8&#42; %0 to i64&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00769" /><CodeLine lineNumber="769"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %4 = load i64, i64&#42; %2</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00770" /><CodeLine lineNumber="770"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %5 = load i64, i64&#42; %3</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00771" /><CodeLine lineNumber="771"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %6 = call i64 @llvm.bswap.i64(i64 %4)</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00772" /><CodeLine lineNumber="772"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %7 = call i64 @llvm.bswap.i64(i64 %5)</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00773" /><CodeLine lineNumber="773"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %8 = sub i64 %6, %7</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00774" /><CodeLine lineNumber="774"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %9 = icmp ne i64 %8, 0</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00775" /><CodeLine lineNumber="775"><Highlight kind="comment">///  br i1 %9, label %res&#95;block, label %loadbb1</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00776" /><CodeLine lineNumber="776"><Highlight kind="comment">/// res&#95;block:                                        ; preds = %loadbb2,</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00777" /><CodeLine lineNumber="777"><Highlight kind="comment">/// %loadbb1, %loadbb</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00778" /><CodeLine lineNumber="778"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %phi.src1 = phi i64 &#91; %6, %loadbb &#93;, &#91; %22, %loadbb1 &#93;, &#91; %36, %loadbb2 &#93;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00779" /><CodeLine lineNumber="779"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %phi.src2 = phi i64 &#91; %7, %loadbb &#93;, &#91; %23, %loadbb1 &#93;, &#91; %37, %loadbb2 &#93;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00780" /><CodeLine lineNumber="780"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %10 = icmp ult i64 %phi.src1, %phi.src2</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00781" /><CodeLine lineNumber="781"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %11 = select i1 %10, i32 -1, i32 1</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00782" /><CodeLine lineNumber="782"><Highlight kind="comment">///  br label %endblock</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00783" /><CodeLine lineNumber="783"><Highlight kind="comment">/// loadbb1:                                          ; preds = %loadbb</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00784" /><CodeLine lineNumber="784"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %12 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer2 to i8&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00785" /><CodeLine lineNumber="785"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %13 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer1 to i8&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00786" /><CodeLine lineNumber="786"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %14 = bitcast i8&#42; %13 to i32&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00787" /><CodeLine lineNumber="787"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %15 = bitcast i8&#42; %12 to i32&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00788" /><CodeLine lineNumber="788"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %16 = getelementptr i32, i32&#42; %14, i32 2</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00789" /><CodeLine lineNumber="789"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %17 = getelementptr i32, i32&#42; %15, i32 2</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00790" /><CodeLine lineNumber="790"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %18 = load i32, i32&#42; %16</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00791" /><CodeLine lineNumber="791"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %19 = load i32, i32&#42; %17</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00792" /><CodeLine lineNumber="792"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %20 = call i32 @llvm.bswap.i32(i32 %18)</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00793" /><CodeLine lineNumber="793"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %21 = call i32 @llvm.bswap.i32(i32 %19)</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00794" /><CodeLine lineNumber="794"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %22 = zext i32 %20 to i64</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00795" /><CodeLine lineNumber="795"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %23 = zext i32 %21 to i64</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00796" /><CodeLine lineNumber="796"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %24 = sub i64 %22, %23</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00797" /><CodeLine lineNumber="797"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %25 = icmp ne i64 %24, 0</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00798" /><CodeLine lineNumber="798"><Highlight kind="comment">///  br i1 %25, label %res&#95;block, label %loadbb2</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00799" /><CodeLine lineNumber="799"><Highlight kind="comment">/// loadbb2:                                          ; preds = %loadbb1</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00800" /><CodeLine lineNumber="800"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %26 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer2 to i8&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00801" /><CodeLine lineNumber="801"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %27 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer1 to i8&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00802" /><CodeLine lineNumber="802"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %28 = bitcast i8&#42; %27 to i16&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00803" /><CodeLine lineNumber="803"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %29 = bitcast i8&#42; %26 to i16&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00804" /><CodeLine lineNumber="804"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %30 = getelementptr i16, i16&#42; %28, i16 6</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00805" /><CodeLine lineNumber="805"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %31 = getelementptr i16, i16&#42; %29, i16 6</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00806" /><CodeLine lineNumber="806"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %32 = load i16, i16&#42; %30</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00807" /><CodeLine lineNumber="807"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %33 = load i16, i16&#42; %31</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00808" /><CodeLine lineNumber="808"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %34 = call i16 @llvm.bswap.i16(i16 %32)</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00809" /><CodeLine lineNumber="809"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %35 = call i16 @llvm.bswap.i16(i16 %33)</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00810" /><CodeLine lineNumber="810"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %36 = zext i16 %34 to i64</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00811" /><CodeLine lineNumber="811"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %37 = zext i16 %35 to i64</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00812" /><CodeLine lineNumber="812"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %38 = sub i64 %36, %37</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00813" /><CodeLine lineNumber="813"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %39 = icmp ne i64 %38, 0</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00814" /><CodeLine lineNumber="814"><Highlight kind="comment">///  br i1 %39, label %res&#95;block, label %loadbb3</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00815" /><CodeLine lineNumber="815"><Highlight kind="comment">/// loadbb3:                                          ; preds = %loadbb2</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00816" /><CodeLine lineNumber="816"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %40 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer2 to i8&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00817" /><CodeLine lineNumber="817"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %41 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer1 to i8&#42;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00818" /><CodeLine lineNumber="818"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %42 = getelementptr i8, i8&#42; %41, i8 14</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00819" /><CodeLine lineNumber="819"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %43 = getelementptr i8, i8&#42; %40, i8 14</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00820" /><CodeLine lineNumber="820"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %44 = load i8, i8&#42; %42</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00821" /><CodeLine lineNumber="821"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %45 = load i8, i8&#42; %43</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00822" /><CodeLine lineNumber="822"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %46 = zext i8 %44 to i32</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00823" /><CodeLine lineNumber="823"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %47 = zext i8 %45 to i32</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00824" /><CodeLine lineNumber="824"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %48 = sub i32 %46, %47</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00825" /><CodeLine lineNumber="825"><Highlight kind="comment">///  br label %endblock</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00826" /><CodeLine lineNumber="826"><Highlight kind="comment">/// endblock:                                         ; preds = %res&#95;block,</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00827" /><CodeLine lineNumber="827"><Highlight kind="comment">/// %loadbb3</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00828" /><CodeLine lineNumber="828"><Highlight kind="comment">///  %phi.res = phi i32 &#91; %48, %loadbb3 &#93;, &#91; %11, %res&#95;block &#93;</Highlight></CodeLine>
